		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/05/23/today-in-small-business-the-rest-of-america/" data-title="Today in Small Business: The Rest of America" data-description="The pros and cons of being a small-business owner. Fred Wilson says it&#039;s a sad day for patent reform. Chasing new markets in India.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A closely watched manufacturing index <a href="//www.marketwatch.com/story/markit-final-manufacturing-pmi-moves-higher-in-may-2014-05-22?si">moved higher</a> in May.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ April sales of existing homes showed <a href="//www.marketwired.com/press-release/april-existing-home-sales-show-modest-improvement-behind-gaining-inventory-1913283.htm">modest improvement</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Janet Yellen <a href="//www.livetradingnews.com/janet-yellen-explains-the-fed-new-full-employment-definition-50669.htm#.U38ZcPk7t8F">explains</a> the Federal Reserveâs new definition of full employment.</p>
